metadata.name: FitNest #1
metadata.description: FitNest is a collection of 1500 MetaCards that grants holders accessibility to the best fitness app in Web3. Alongside of additional tangible utilities and virtual opportunities and the ability to rent their card out to visitors at our in person gyms. Our goal is to bring health and fitness into the MetaVerse both physically and mentally creating a positive healthy space for individuals. Learn more about us on our website at FitNestOfficial.com or join our Discord at Discord.gg/FitNest.
